title: Ruffled Feathers Rising for Mac
description: In Ruffled: Feathers Rising, you soar through the skies of Splat City as a bird with a very "fowl" temper! Sick of the humans and armed with a cranky large intestine, you gobble down some fat juicy worms and head out to fight back in the only manner that you know how... Ya... we went there! So grab your copy and experience Splat City from a stylized birds eye view and find out just how satisfying it can be to... well... you know...
